text: We ordered the BBQ wings. Seems tough, maybe cos it was reheated in the micro wave. The fried wings are reheated by frying again. Saw alot of pple buying their spaghetti. 5.90 for mushroom spaghetti. 6.90 for cream chicken spaghetti, 8.90 for mushroom and chicken.
Tender chicken cutlet served with rice, sunny side up and coleslaw. 👍👍👍
Decent portions & tasty plate of roasted chicken w yellow rice, fried chicken also not bad too 😍😍😍
The chicken chop is very tender.
Convenient outlet, fantastic array of choices, taste very good, reasonable price.  A little hot even with fans
